r_black-studio-top-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Hope-Tech-3-Duo-double-hydraulic-disc-brake_2-brakes-2-levers-1-hand_Hopetech-CNC-machined-dual-hydraulic-brake-lever_black-studio-top-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Hope-Tech-3-Duo-double-hydraulic-disc-brake_2-brakes-2-levers-1-hand_Hopetech-CNC-machined-dual-hydraulic-brake-lever_black-studio-top-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Hope-Tech-3-Duo-double-hydraulic-disc-brake_2-brakes-2-levers-1-hand_Hopetech-CNC-machined-dual-hydraulic-brake-lever_black-studio-top-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Hope-Tech-3-Duo-double-hydraulic-disc-brake_2-brakes-2-levers-1-hand_Hopetech-CNC-machined-dual-hydraulic-brake-lever_black-studio-top-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-227944\">Not seen the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/11/25/hope-tech-3-duo-lever-pulls-2-hydraulic-brakes-with-1-hand-tech-3-x2-uno-does-too/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hope Tech 3 Duo</a> brake yet? This is two brakes in one, with two levers operated by one hand!</figcaption></figure><p>Laser cut from a sheet of custom steel, Hope designed the V4 rotor with their V-Series downhill, enduro and eMTB brakes in mind. Available as a 6-bolt design only, get it in 180mm, 200mm and 220mm diameters for £40.00 / €50.00 / $50.00 (excluding tax).&nbsp;<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><h3>Hope Technology Bosch Kiox Headunit Display Mount</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/20