ech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-297x298.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-800x803.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-768x771.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-696x699.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-1068x1072.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/hope-tech-ebike-computer-display-bosch-kiosk-headunit-418x420.jpg 418w\"></a></p><p>Hope have CNC machined some head unit display mounts for the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/07/07/bosch-cx-boosts-torque-gets-new-hi-res-displays-navigation-in-e-bike-drive-updates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bosch Kiox</a>. Anodized in six Hope signature colors, the mount for the stem only and has the exact same rise as the original Bosch mount. Pick one up for £65.00 / €80.00 / $82.00 (excluding tax).</p><p><a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>HopeTech.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"76b51413e0244bc7adf7a7e677c84c357432dda081608f05eab1f4a9c5600e51","category":"Cycling"}